_:b0__277 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Källa: Bostadsmarknadsenkäten"@sv;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U30465> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-05-13"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Kommunen har goda möjligheter att erbjuda anvisade nyanlända bostad, (Ja=1, Nej=0)"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/GOVE>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/REGI>, _:b0__806;
