<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#e796ad752a4662a211270f475117d727>.
<#e796ad752a4662a211270f475117d727> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N00373>;
