    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__4638.
_:b0__4638 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2099-12-31"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2001-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/1054> <http://entryscape.org/terms/metadataIdentifier> "358ac010-28e7-48f5-98c6-12aa1e4c64be";
