<https://doi.org/10.48723/4xbv-q790> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Depression"@sv, "Depression"@en, "Ångest"@sv, "Anxiety"@en, "Internet-Based Intervention"@en, "Internetbaserad intervention"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__8820.
_:b0__8820 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/6639e44f50ff72a27d22f24d4c2ea359>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.48723/4xbv-q790> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__33461.
_:b0__33461 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/dc2a1a40dced684301d881860fd93f68>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.48723/4xbv-q790> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/NON_PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021002973>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The dataset consists of participant-level data from a randomized feasibility study of a digital self-help intervention for anxiety and depression. It includes clinical measures, demographic information, and treatment group assignment for 124 participants.\n\nThe data are provided in two files:\n\ndata_tailored_selfhelp_depanx.csv — the main dataset, containing variables such as gender, age, marital status, education, employment status, economic situation, diagnostic information, and repeated measures of symptoms and functioning over time (PHQ-9, GAD-7, WHODAS). Additionally, it includes variables on intervention satisfaction (CSQ-8) and treatment credibility (CEQ).\n\ndata_description.csv — a data dictionary describing all variables, their types, coding, and meaning. This file facilitates interpretation of the values in the dataset."@en, "Datamaterialet består av deltagarnivådata från en randomiserad genomförbarhetsstudie av en digital själv-hjälpsintervention för ångest och depression. Datasetet innehåller kliniska mått, demografisk information och behandlingsgruppstillhörighet för 124 deltagare.\n\nData finns i två filer:\n\ndata_tailored_selfhelp_depanx.csv — huvuddatasetet med variabler som kön, ålder, civilstånd, utbildning, sysselsättningsstatus, ekonomisk situation, diagnostiska uppgifter samt skattningar av symtom och funktionsnedsättning över tid (PHQ-9, GAD-7, WHODAS). Dessutom finns variabler som n��jdhet med interventionen (CSQ-8) samt interventionens trovärdighet (CEQ) med.\n\ndata_description.csv — data dictionary som beskriver alla variabler, deras typer, kodning och betydelse. Denna fil gör det lätt att tolka värdena i datasetet."@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/2661886>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/13f252589ea011ab016c39940138f349>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.48723/4xbv-q790#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-10-03T08:18:27.456489Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.48723/4xbv-q790>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-05T13:38:41.030897Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Data for: Tailored digital self-help for anxiety and depression: A randomized feasibility trial with or without guidance"@en, "Data för: Tailored digital self-help for anxiety and depression: A randomized feasibility trial with or without guidance"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/SOCI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/HEAL>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
}

