<https://metadata.lidingo.se/dataset/postlista-for-lidingo-stad-och-valnamnden/resource/291a33ed-0e99-45db-be8f-a2406980a45d> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>;
